fetchLines

java.util.ArrayList<LineInterface> fetchLines(BridgeConstants.Side side)
Gets the existing lines of a budget. The returned array list is intended to be immutable. To add / delete a line use the add / delete methods and invoke this method again to get the updated line array list.

Parameters:
